{"id":4040,"date":"2021-11-12T04:15:01","date_gmt":"2021-11-12T04:15:01","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/?p=4040"},"modified":"2021-11-18T14:54:00","modified_gmt":"2021-11-18T14:54:00","slug":"meriah-balinosa-2021-kini-beda-digelar-secara-hybrid","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/2021\/11\/12\/meriah-balinosa-2021-kini-beda-digelar-secara-hybrid\/","title":{"rendered":"Meriah! BALINOSA 2021 Kini Beda, Digelar Secara Hybrid"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Balinosa 2021 (Bazzar Literasi November Satu) Kembali digelar disaat pandemi covid-19 secara hybrid<br>.<br>Balinosa 2021 adalah program unggulan sekolah dalam bidang literasi dan kewirausahaan dimana setiap kelas mengirimkan perwakilan nya untuk mengukiti 5 Lomba diantara nya:<br>1. Penampilan Kelas<br>2. Business Plan<br>3. News Anchor<br>4. Cerpen<br>5. Puisi<br>Menurut Deddy Kepala SMA Negeri 1 Bandung. \u201cProduk yang di pasarkan siswa melalui media sosial mampu bersaing dengan produk-produk ternama bahkan dapat dikatakan kemasan dan rasa nya seperti produk premium\u201d. Ujarnya.<br>dibuka oleh Eskul LSS Balinosa semakin meriah walaupun secara virtual.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"[\ud83d\udd34LIVE] BALINOSA 2021 (DAY 1) - Penampilan kelas dan news anchor\" width=\"1020\" height=\"574\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/1T_xRwkV7vA?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"[\ud83d\udd34LIVE] BALINOSA 2021 (DAY 2) Penampilan kelas dan news anchor\" width=\"1020\"